Package: hcruR
Title: Estimate and Compare Healthcare Resource Utilization (HCRU) for RWE
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Maheshkumar", "Umbarkar", email = "maheshubr30@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to estimate and compare healthcare resource utilization (HCRU) by domain and cohort. Supports cohort-based event counting, cost summarization, time window analysis, and plotting for RWE studies.
